para_trans: Government Corrigendum No. Rajbh - 2021/399 P.C. 976 / Rajbh
Read: - General Administration Department, Government Decisions, No. January 8, 2025.

The revised profile of the posts in the Raj Bhavan Office has been fixed by the Government Decision dated 08.01.2025 in reference. The revised pay scale of the posts mentioned in the following column (b) of the profile of the Office of the Family Manager to the Governor in the statement "B" accompanying the said Government decision should be read as in column (a) of the Table: -

The Government Corrigendum is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
